Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.51,op-J,,0,0,0,,羽ばたいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.51,op-C,,0,0,0,,展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.64,op-J,,0,0,0,,負けそうでも逃げたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.64,op-C,,0,0,0,,無論如何決不逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.88,op-J,,0,0,0,,君と刻む時を信じていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.88,op-C,,0,0,0,,堅信與你共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:25.37,op-J,,0,0,0,,君と刻む時を信じていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:25.37,op-C,,0,0,0,,堅信與你共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:27.73,op-J,,0,0,0,,光まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:27.73,op-C,,0,0,0,,直到光明的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.24,op-J,,0,0,0,,笑顔と涙を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.24,op-C,,0,0,0,,將笑容與淚水擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:36.70,op-J,,0,0,0,,大切な人守る為に強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:36.69,op-C,,0,0,0,,為了保護珍愛的人而變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.62,ed-J,,0,0,0,,高く　もっとbeautiful sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.62,ed-C,,0,0,0,,飛向更高更美的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:18.64,ed-J,,0,0,0,,透き通る眼差しへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:18.64,ed-C,,0,0,0,,進入清澈透明的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:19.88,ed-J,,0,0,0,,守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:19.88,ed-C,,0,0,0,,想要守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:23.80,ed-J,,0,0,0,,輝きが今日も 力になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:23.80,ed-C,,0,0,0,,今日的光輝也將化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:26.75,ed-J,,0,0,0,,輝きが今日も 力になるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:26.75,ed-C,,0,0,0,,今日的光輝也將化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:41.14,ed-J,,0,0,0,,並んだ風に　君を感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:41.14,ed-C,,0,0,0,,在拂過的清風中感受到你的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:45.55,ed-J,,0,0,0,,存在がうれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:45.55,ed-C,,0,0,0,,你的存在讓我如此陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:48.96,ed-J,,0,0,0,,しんかくして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:48.96,ed-C,,0,0,0,,想要一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:56.08,ed-J,,0,0,0,,見上げる空は毎日違うかもなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:56.08,ed-C,,0,0,0,,仰望的天空今日也必將不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:57.25,ed-J,,0,0,0,,どこまでも行けるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:57.25,ed-C,,0,0,0,,我們能去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:59.23,ed-J,,0,0,0,,どこまでも行けるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:59.23,ed-C,,0,0,0,,我們能去任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:01.80,ed-J,,0,0,0,,描いてくここから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:01.80,ed-C,,0,0,0,,現在開始描繪未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.62,ed-J,,0,0,0,,気が愛より強い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:03.62,ed-C,,0,0,0,,有了愛我們能夠做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:05.30,ed-J,,0,0,0,,自分でいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:05.30,ed-C,,0,0,0,,因為我們就是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:08.14,ed-J,,0,0,0,,いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:08.14,ed-C,,0,0,0,,直到永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.55,ed-J,,0,0,0,,高く　もっとbeautiful sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.55,ed-C,,0,0,0,,飛向更高更美的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.65,ed-J,,0,0,0,,透き通る眼差しに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.65,ed-C,,0,0,0,,進入清澈透明的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:18.82,ed-J,,0,0,0,,この瞬間を焼き付けていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:18.82,ed-C,,0,0,0,,將這一瞬間永遠銘記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:22.19,ed-J,,0,0,0,,光り　もっとbeautiful sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.31,0:23:22.19,ed-C,,0,0,0,,飛向閃亮美麗的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:25.25,ed-J,,0,0,0,,翼ごと抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:25.25,ed-C,,0,0,0,,將你和翅膀一同抱緊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:26.80,ed-J,,0,0,0,,守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:26.80,ed-C,,0,0,0,,永遠守護著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:33.27,ed-J,,0,0,0,,輝きが今日も力をくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:33.27,ed-C,,0,0,0,,今日的光輝也將賜予我們力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:52.71,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1525,107)}{\fad(1000,1000)}英雄的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是 喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和我組隊吧 簪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的機體數據 有幫上忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都是…姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不在這
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是 專用機擁有者的組合淘汰賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在場的各同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,現在是展現每日訓練成果…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,簪 去哪兒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對於沒有專用機的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這次比賽內容是一次難得的學習機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好把握哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我的機體數據 有幫上忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼也不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我會全部代勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我… 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣無能下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.32,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我 贏不了那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒想過要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,總之得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 期待大家能度過一段充實的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,請允許我以此作為開場白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 廢話就到這
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現在公佈對戰表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,簪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,難道先去維修站了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,織斑老師 遇到襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟以前出現過的無人機一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不 感覺是升級版
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,幾台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,5台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都在競技場的維修站裏出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,正在攻擊待機中的專用機學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,教師要優先考慮學生避難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥教員 全員 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然來這手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不要小看我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴桑 退後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拉烏拉 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,夏…夏洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那… 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不…  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,織斑君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,簪 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,織斑君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快啟動IS 會被捲進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,織斑君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這個攻擊 好吃力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,向外衝 拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然這麼硬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,箒醬 打開背部展開裝甲 支援我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,楯無桑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,楯無桑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣 擊毀無人機的裝甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,少廢話 就照我說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,給我 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐我的後招 現在才開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,裝甲被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,箒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,防禦全開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要被捲進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐我可是不死身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘗嘗霧纏的淑女最大攻擊的威力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,寄生樹之劍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Mystletainn
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,發動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,難道 箒她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,簪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,織斑君 確認一下對面出入口處的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不會讓你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,敵機IS從手臂處射出未知的能量光波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,密閉防護罩發生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對防禦失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,針對IS的專用IS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,織斑君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢… 竟敢 竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,核心 如果把那個毀掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一…一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,果然做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,救不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一點用也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,存在在這個世界 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個世上 不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多少年 沒這麼叫過我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,做這些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已經不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,才不會不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在這個世界上英雄什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,完美無暇的英雄什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄什麼的 不會哭 也不會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,會哭會笑 也會失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不逃跑 戰鬥下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你不怕死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那還是怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是逃了的話  感覺就變不回原來的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,弱小也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,骯髒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,卑鄙也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,丟人也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,都因為是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,姐…姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 簪醬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,弱小也好 渺小也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都要接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,接受了的話 就能站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因為 是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,還因為是讓我自豪的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我去去就回 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,萬不得已時 用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,液態水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 沒事吧 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,箒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏  零落白夜怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 沒能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那就 用絢爛舞蹈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有人能爭取到時間的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我來爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,簪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,沒功夫猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一夏 伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,打鐵二式 手動誘導系統 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,山嵐彈頭導彈數 48
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,全軌道 手動控制 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,賜予我力量吧 打鐵二式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,紅椿 讓我瞧瞧你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看也看不懂的說明不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,左手 拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,簪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,到護身符出場的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,塞西莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,簪醬 痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不能動的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,傷得不輕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣和簪醬說話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有幾年沒有過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了一夏君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼拜託他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是想對他撒嬌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 臉紅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因…因為夕陽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一…一直以來 很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是個沒用的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…我最重要的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很堅強的 我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 是無人機的發展機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,未登記而得以回收的核心有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,對政府說全都摧毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 那樣的話學校就陷入危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一個兩個學園還是能保護的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,即使拼上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 不好好說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,簪 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 一夏 這…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 如果不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這個好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,以前看過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,最…最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡一夏什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,應該沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒說奇怪的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,動畫 你喜歡這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是只說了喜歡動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃哦 美味哦 健康哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,簪牌夜宵店拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咸味 味噌味 醬油味
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,織斑老師 你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  Infinite Stratos 2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,「cooking my way」
